Package: pishutdown
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.24), procps
Description: Desktop shutdown helper for Raspberry Pi
 Small application offering shutdown / reboot / logout options, run from the
 shutdown option on the main menu.
